nodes.text: An impostor of the Rebel Alliance operative Luke Skywalker lived in the galaxy during the Imperial Era. Around 3 ABY, he boasted in a cantina about his alleged exploits of destroying the Death Star, hoping he could fool bar patrons and be hired as a pilot. When word spread of "Luke Skywalker's" activities, however, Darth Vader confronted the man and killed him for wasting his time.
